results.title: Search for Missing 17-Year-Old Boy

-MozJnnf7jXrbPs8wUg2.text: Police are searching for a missing 17-year-old boy. He is described as Somali, 5'6", and 180 lbs. He was last seen at 11:00 a.m. today wearing a gray shirt with Spongebob on the front, and black and white shorts. Police report that he has Autism.

-MozJxN1cUPmq9K3bjcX.text: Citizen has not received a photo of this missing person. Do you have one? Go to the home screen and tap “Get Agent” to talk to our team. Police are requesting the public to 911 if they see him.

results.title: Person Shot

-MoyxG5V0z09VQJH3UUW.text: Incident reported at 190 Larpenteur Ave W.

-MoyxG8BbkyJUdY4AE6X.text: Police have received an unconfirmed 911 report of three gunshots fired.

-MoyzAGpV3EygCjUGIMA.text: Firefighters on the scene advise that a person was shot following gunshots fired in the building.

-Moz0attYBQVQ9aCDwya.text: Police on the scene advise that a woman has been shot in the leg and police are investigating in the area to see if there are more victims. A fire alarm is sounding in the building but firefighters confirm that there is no fire.

-Moz1nFBPjI9sEmhHEmi.text: A citizen user has shared a video of heavy police response at the scene and an arriving ambulance.

-Moz1sYygkg62CTwUye_.text: Police are undertaking further investigations at the first floor making sure no one else was shot.
